#. type: Plain text
#: ../src/cookbook/custom-migration-template.md
msgid "Keep generated migrations independent from current application services. A migration may run years later, after service APIs have changed. Put stable schema operations in the generated class and leave business logic in console commands or application services."
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: ../src/cookbook/custom-migration-template.md
msgid "Do not edit templates under `vendor/`. Copy them into your project and configure `CreateService` to use the copies."
msgstr ""
